en.description: The Soma Prime is the primed version of the Soma assault rifle. It primarily features a greater magazine size, greater ammo reserves, and a slight increase to physical damage and status chance.
en.codex: Known for taking down whole squads with its single massive clip, few weapons were as feared as the Prime Soma.

ru.description: Известная своей способностью уложить целый отряд за один магазин, Сома Прайм имела немного столь же устрашающих аналогов.
